b'     Dear all   Greetings from NSS family!  NSS IITM is conducting its  General Collection Drive(GCD) 2nd November 2016 (Wednesday) to 5th November 2016 (Saturday)  During the given dates, the volunteers will come to the rooms in the hostel zone and offices in the academic zone and collect items including onesided sheets, clothes, toys, usable footwear, newspaper,usable electronic gadgets andany other nonperishable items that could be of use. Kindly do not give money or any perishable items. Give your signature on the sheet the volunteer produces. Kindly make yourself available in your rooms during these days so that items may be collected. Det ailed instructions for NSSv olunteers will be sent in a separate mail. </span For any queries, feel free to contact Jahnvi 9978907446 Melwin 9497040026    P.S:  It is a credited event for NSS Volunteers.    Thanks and Regards, Managerial team, NSS IIT Madras  Website:  www.nss.iitm.ac.in Facebook:  www.facebook.com/nss.iitm   '

